##### add a new animal
###
POST http://localhost:3000/add-animal?idir={{idir}} HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
  "animal_id": "test123",
  "animal_status": "Alive",
  "calf_at_heel": true,
  "species": "unicorn",
  "sex": "M",
  "wlh_id": "abc123",
  "nickname": "shimmer"
}

### add existing animal, species should remain "wolf", sex "M"
POST http://localhost:3000/add-animal?idir={{idir}} HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
  "animal_id": "test123",
  "animal_status": "Alive",
  "calf_at_heel": true,
  "sex": "M",
  "wlh_id": "abc123",
  "nickname": "shimmer",
  "id": 2
}

##### get animals
###
http://localhost:3000/get-animals?idir={{idir}}

### get specific id
http://localhost:3000/animal/3

### get page 1
http://localhost:3000/get-animals?idir={{idir}}&page=1

### page 2
http://localhost:3000/get-animals?idir={{idir}}&page=2